title: Woolley's
typeOfFood: Western, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small lunch joint in Holborn that also operates as a local office caterer. Has an entirely vegetarian salad bar; a soup of the day that is always vegetarian and sometimes vegan; baked potatoes with a variety of toppings; and a hot food bar that always has at least a couple vegan choices such as dahl, chilli, or tagine. Veg/vegan is labeled.
